# 处理时间格式
for item in item_info.find({},{'pub_time':1,'_id':1}):
    print(item)
    if item['pub_time'] is not None:
        pub_date_str = item['pub_time'].split(' ') [0].split('-')
        length = len(pub_date_str)
        print(item)
        print(pub_date_str)
        if length >1:

            month = int(pub_date_str[0])
            day = int(pub_date_str[1])
            
            if month >1:
                year = 2015
            else:
                year = 2016
            if month<10:
                month = '0'+str(month)
            if day<10:
                day = '0'+str(day)
            dates = '{}.{}.{}'.format(year,month,day)
            print(date)
            item_info.update_one({'_id':item['_id']},{'$set':{'pub_time':dates}})
        else :
            item_info.update_one({'_id':item['_id']},{'$set':{'pub_time':None}})

# 获取两个时间段内的所有日期
def get_all_dates(date1,date2):
    start_date = date(int(date1.split('.')[0]),int(date1.split('.')[1]),int(date1.split('.')[2]))
    end_date = date(int(date2.split('.')[0]),int(date2.split('.')[1]),int(date2.split('.')[2]))
    days = timedelta(days=1)
    while start_date<=end_date:
        dates = start_date.strftime('%Y.%m.%d')
        yield dates
        start_date+=days

        { '$match':{'cate':'二手设备/办公用品','new_old':{'$in':['6岁以上', '1-3岁']}}},

for item in item_info.aggregate(pipline):

In [209]:
def get_series(cate):
    
    pipline = [

            { '$match':{'cate':cate}},

            {'$group':{

                      '_id':{'new_old':'$new_old'},
                    'avg_price':{'$avg':'$price'}
                }},

        ]
#     return  item_info.aggregate(pipline)
     
    data_list = []
    for item in item_info.aggregate(pipline):
        data_list.append(int(item['avg_price']))
    print(data_list)
    datas ={
        'name':cate,
        'data':data_list,
        'type': 'line'

    }

    return  datas
In [215]:
def get_all_new_old(cate):
    
    pipline = [

            { '$match':{'cate':cate}},

            {'$group':{

                      '_id':{'new_old':'$new_old'},
                    'avg_price':{'$avg':'$price'}
                }},

        ]
#     return  item_info.aggregate(pipline)
     
    data_list = []
    for item in item_info.aggregate(pipline):
        data_list.append((item['_id']['new_old']))
    print(data_list)

    return  data_list
